Description: The Fairy Tail are a group of powerful wizards.
Title: FAIRY TAIL, VOL. 19
Author: Hiro Mashima

Description: These crime stories are set in a future (year 2030) version of Japan. Will the task force be able track down the serial killer and hacker "The Laughing Man"?
Title: GHOST IN THE SHELL: STAND ALONE COMPLEX, VOL. 3
Author: Yu Kinutani

Description: From the publisher: "Nanami is shocked to discover that the townsfolk consider her shrine abandoned." Will her work to revitalize the shrine pay off?
Title: KAMISAMA KISS, VOL. 9
Author: Julietta Suzuki

Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 40
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: Welcome to Todo High, whose student body is composed of the toughest of brawlers.
Title: TENJO TENGE, VOL. 7
Author: Oh! Great Staff

Description: High school student by day, genius hacker by night. Takagi Fujimaru and friends band together to stop a terrorist group from murdering millions of people in Tokyo.
Title: BLOODY MONDAY, VOL. 6
Author: Ryou Ryumon

Description: Yuma Tsukumo will stop at nothing to become the Duel Masters champion, but as a rank amateur, the odds are stacked against him. Luckily, he has a mysterious spirit named Astral to help him.
Title: YU-GI-OH! ZEXAL, VOL. 1
Author: Kazuki Takahashi, Shin Yoshida and Naohito Miyoshi
Contributor: by Kazuki Takahashi, Shin Yoshida and Naohito Miyoshi

Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 41
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: In this romantic comedy, Haruhi, a poor girl at a rich school, is forced to work — as a boy — for the school’s all-male club.
Title: OURAN HIGH SCHOOL HOST CLUB, VOL. 18
Author: Bisco Hatori

Description: Naruto and his allies face off against a horde of ninja soldiers, some of whom are back from the dead and former friends.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 56
Author: Masashi Kishimoto
